      <summary>Are these aligned with the latest GCP guidelines?</summary>
      <p>Each SOP is built on ICH E6(R2) with E6(R3) guidance notes, referencing 21 CFR Parts 11, 50, 56, and 312 as well as 45 CFR Part 46 where applicable.</p>
